(20, 1, '2014-10-21 15:38:40', '2014-10-21 15:38:40', '<h1>Coordinated<br /><em>Consultancy</em></h1>\r\n<p>We provide high quality coordinated project, management and property consultancy services that support our clients’ in achieving their built environment aspirations on new projects, refurbishment schemes and estates rationalisation.</p>\r\n<p>Our tailored solutions are applied with ingenuity through our main services, see below.</p>', 'Building Consultancy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'building-consultancy', '', '', '2014-11-06 17:47:46', '2014-11-06 17:47:46', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?page_id=20', 2, 'page', '', 0),
