(36, 1, '2014-10-21 15:46:54', '2014-10-21 15:46:54', '<h1>Coordinated<br /><em>Consultancy</em></h1>\r\n<p>Our building surveying team is experienced in looking after wide range of buildings to support owners, occupiers and investors with the purchase, maintenance, management, rationalisation, enhancement and disposal of their built assets. Lead by RICS chartered building surveyors our team includes cost, access, sustainability, structural and building services consultants. This allows us to deliver a comprehensive and coordinated range of specialist services across the UK including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>· Estate rationalisation surveys / multi facet surveys / property strategies</li>\r\n<li>· Building surveys</li>\r\n<li>· Design and refurbishment</li>\r\n<li>· Rights to light / sunlight daylight assessments</li>\r\n<li>· Access consultancy</li>\r\n<li>· Dilapidations</li>\r\n<li>· Fire risk assessments</li>\r\n<li>· Expert witness</li>\r\n<li>· Conservation consultancy</li>\r\n<li>· Bank fund monitoring</li>\r\n<li>· Building cost reinstatement valuation Cost consultancy</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Services', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'building-surveyors', '', '', '2014-11-04 09:16:33', '2014-11-04 09:16:33', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?page_id=36', 0, 'page', '', 0),
