(56, 1, '2014-10-21 22:26:31', '2014-10-21 22:26:31', '<h1>Celebrating success </h1>\r\n<p>Development of the Year 2014 - Albion Place, Skipton. Yorkshire Business Insider Property Awards</p>\r\n<p>Highly Commended 2014 - Architecture Firm of the Year. <br />Yorkshire Business Insider Property Awards</p>\r\n<p>Good Employers Guide 2014 - 2009. Building Magazine</p>\r\n<p>Tourism and Leisure High Commendation 2013 – Cavendish Pavilion, Bolton Abbey. <br />RICS Pro-Yorkshire Awards</p>\r\n<p>Community Award 2012 – Culture Fusion, Bradford. LABC Building Excellence Awards</p>\r\n<p>Commercial Award 2012 - Wm Morrison Supermarket, Newport. LABC Building Excellence Awards</p>\r\n<p>Restoration Special Commendation 2012 - Greenroyd Mill, Craven. <br />Yorkshire Business Insider Property Awards</p>\r\n<p>Residential High Commendation 2012 - Greenroyd Mill, Craven. RICS Pro-Yorkshire Awards</p>\r\n<p>Commercial Award 2011 HML. Headquarters Building, Skipton. RICS Pro-Yorkshire Awards</p>\r\n<p>Design Award 2011 - The Nell Bank. Centre, Ilkley. Ilkley Civic Society</p>\r\n<p>Best Architect 2010. Variety Club Yorkshire Property Awards</p>\r\n<p>Architects Practice of the Year 2009. Yorkshire Insider Property Industry Awards</p>\r\n<p>Office Development of the Year 2009. Toronto Square, Leeds. Estates Gazette Green Awards</p>', 'Our Awards', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'our-awards', '', '', '2014-11-10 12:00:13', '2014-11-10 12:00:13', '', 2, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?page_id=56', 2, 'page', '', 0),
