(61, 1, '2014-10-22 08:21:26', '2014-10-22 08:21:26', '<p>After working in Montego Bay, Jamaica, Matthew joined Bowman Riley Architects in 1997. He established the central Leeds office over ten years ago and the London office in 2012. He manages both teams specialising in commercial, retail, residential and industrial projects. Matthew is a keen golfer, former rugby player and enjoys live music.</p>', 'Matthew Jones', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'matthew-jones', '', '', '2014-11-11 11:12:12', '2014-11-11 11:12:12', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=61', 0, 'people', '', 0),
(62, 1, '2014-10-22 08:29:59', '2014-10-22 08:29:59', '<p>MSc, PhD in Catalyst for Change &amp; Infrastructure (ongoing)</p>\r\n<p>Karl has over 20 years of property experience ranging from estate rationalisation, finance, strategic/commercial planning and analysis. He is passionate about BIM and is a Director of the UK BIM4SME group; the core cities agenda; procurement; MMC and cloud based technologies. He is also a Fellow of the Leeds Sustainability Institute. Karl enjoys running, rowing, reading, golf and provides coaching in football and basketball. He likes to spend as much as he can with his children.</p>', 'Karl Redmond', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'karl-redmond', '', '', '2014-11-11 11:10:45', '2014-11-11 11:10:45', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=62', 0, 'people', '', 0),
