(75, 1, '2014-10-22 19:51:19', '2014-10-22 19:51:19', '<p>MCIAT</p>\r\n<p>Mark joined in January 2011 to establish Bowman Riley Healthcare with fellow director, Steve Batson. With over 26 years’ experience working within the healthcare sector, his focus is on the client care and the technical delivery of projects. Mark is a keen golfer, cricketer and supporter of his home football club Huddersfield Town.</p>', 'Mark Dean', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mark-dean', '', '', '2014-11-11 11:08:00', '2014-11-11 11:08:00', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=75', 0, 'people', '', 0),
(76, 1, '2014-10-22 19:51:40', '2014-10-22 19:51:40', '<p>Bsc (Hons) FRICS, BREEAM Assessor,</p>\r\n<p>Working at Bowman Riley since 2005, Debbie champions sustainable design by positively influencing our clients to improve the sustainability of their projects, estates and operations and by raising awareness of environmental issues amongst our teams. As a key member of the Building Consultancy team, Debbie has delivered a range of services including building and party wall surveying, project management, access consultancy and BREEAM assessments. Debbie is a member of the RICS Yorkshire and Humberside Regional Board, chairs the regional RICS Commercial Group and is an RICS Associate Assessor. Debbie enjoys industrial antiques restoration and ice skating.</p>', 'Debbie Lewis', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'debbie-lewis', '', '', '2014-11-11 11:05:02', '2014-11-11 11:05:02', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=76', 0, 'people', '', 0),
(77, 1, '2014-10-22 19:52:18', '2014-10-22 19:52:18', '<p>MSc BSc</p>\r\n<p>Robert began working at Bowman Riley Architects following completion of his Master’s degree in Project Management in 2013. During his career, Robert has gained experience on a wide variety of projects ranging from large multi-million pound new build projects to small low cost refurbishment schemes performing the roles of project manager and building surveyor. Hobbies</p>', 'Robert Catton', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'robert-catton', '', '', '2014-11-10 17:00:50', '2014-11-10 17:00:50', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=77', 0, 'people', '', 0),
(78, 1, '2014-10-22 19:52:33', '2014-10-22 19:52:33', '<p>MRICS MAPM</p>\r\n<p>With 20 years’ experience at Bowman Riley, Robin established and heads up Bowman Riley Building Consultancy, which provides a comprehensive range of building surveying, project management, health and safety, estates, facilities and sustainability consultancy services. Originating from the Yorkshire Dales, Robin enjoys sport and time spent outdoors, walking and travelling with his family.</p>', 'Robin Holme', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'robin-holme', '', '', '2014-11-11 11:02:40', '2014-11-11 11:02:40', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=78', 0, 'people', '', 0),
