(215, 1, '2014-10-24 18:33:09', '2014-10-24 18:33:09', '<h1>Project Management</h1>\r\n<p>Our team of qualified project managers have wide ranging experience in leading the successful delivery of projects on time, within budget and to the highest of standards.</p>\r\n<p>Our client focused methods are proven, allowing our enthusiastic hands-on professional project managers to motivate the whole team, minimise risks and exceed expectations whilst delivering your projects.</p>\r\n<p>Our services include:</p>\r\n<p>Project Management · Programme management · Employers agent · Contract administration · Risk management · Move management · Feasibility studies / option appraisals / Estate rationalisation · Fund / development monitoring · Technical Advisor · Independent certifier · Full design, management and property consultancy service.</p>', 'Project Management', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'project-management', '', '', '2014-11-04 21:05:24', '2014-11-04 21:05:24', '', 20, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?page_id=215', 1, 'page', '', 0),
