(226, 1, '2014-10-29 13:11:43', '2014-10-29 13:11:43', '<h1>DELIVERING THOUGHTFUL &amp; RESPONSIVE DESIGN SINCE 1968</h1>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley provides innovative architecture and integrated building consultancy operating across the UK. With over 45 years’ experience, our award winning team of 70 continues to successfully deliver a range of projects that transform our clients’ visions into reality. Our approach is to combine design excellence with practical expertise founded on solid commercial knowledge that ensures our projects are both realistic and achievable.</p>', 'All About Bowman Riley', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-29 13:11:43', '2014-10-29 13:11:43', '', 2, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(227, 1, '2014-10-29 13:14:46', '2014-10-29 13:14:46', '<h1>Our Story</h1>\r\n<p>In 1968 three architects decided to launch a new practice and unable to decide on where to locate the Head Office to best serve the commercial centres of Leeds and Manchester, a pin was stuck in a map somewhere in between. The market town Skipton, on the edge of the Yorkshire Dales was picked and there our story began.</p>\r\n<p>From the beginning the practice has had a very clear, unswerving, focus on quality design, attention to detail and client care, so much so that we continue to work with long standing clients, some of whom span back to our company’s inception.</p>\r\n<p>Today Bowman Riley is a dynamic and commercial practice led by directors Darren Bush, John Coultas, Michael Feather, Matthew Jones and Laurence Teeney operating from offices in Leeds, London and Skipton. To complement our design services, we offer a range of Building Consultancy services led by Robin Holme.</p>\r\n<p>In 2010 Steve Batson and Mark Dean joined our family and launched Bowman Riley Healthcare Architects to meet the needs of this specialist market.</p>', 'Our Story', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '6-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-29 13:14:46', '2014-10-29 13:14:46', '', 6, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/6-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(228, 1, '2014-10-29 13:18:45', '2014-10-29 13:18:45', '<h1>COMMERCIALLY<br />CREATIVE<br /><em>ARCHITECTS</em></h1>\r\n<p>A commitment to high quality and innovative design is at the very heart of the projects we create.</p>\r\n<p>With significant experience in the delivery of a wide range of new and refurbished buildings, we help our clients realise their built environment aspirations.</p>\r\n<p>From small complex projects to multi-million pound developments and roll-out programmes, our team has the practical expertise to take a project from concept planning to completion on site.</p>', 'Architects', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '18-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-29 13:18:45', '2014-10-29 13:18:45', '', 18, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/18-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(229, 1, '2014-10-29 13:19:39', '2014-10-29 13:19:39', '<h1>COMMERCIALLY<br />CREATIVE<br /><em>ARCHITECTS</em></h1>\r\n<p>A commitment to high quality and innovative design is at the very heart of the projects we create.</p>\r\n<p>With significant experience in the delivery of a wide range of new and refurbished buildings, we help our clients realise their built environment aspirations.</p>\r\n<p>From small complex projects to multi-million pound developments and roll-out programmes, our team has the practical expertise to take a project from concept planning to completion on site.</p>\r\n<p>Working in partnership with our clients and the wider design and construction team, we strive to lead the way in terms of innovation, efficiency and sustainability to deliver tangible benefits for our clients.</p>\r\n<p>Please explore our services and case studies for more information.</p>', 'Architects', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '18-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-29 13:19:39', '2014-10-29 13:19:39', '', 18, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/18-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(230, 1, '2014-10-29 13:24:08', '2014-10-29 13:24:08', '<h1>Headline Before<br /><em>Building Consultants</em></h1>\n<p>We provide high quality coordinated project, management and property consultancy services that support our clients’ in achieving their built environment aspirations on new projects, refurbishment schemes and estates rationalisation.</p>\n<p>Our tailored solutions are applied with ingenuity through our main services:</p>\n<p>Building Surveying</p>\n<p>Project Management Cost Consultancy Health &amp; Safety Sustainability Estate and Facilities Consultancy</p>', 'Building Consultancy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '20-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-29 13:24:08', '2014-10-29 13:24:08', '', 20, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/20-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
