(378, 1, '2014-10-29 20:26:54', '2014-10-29 20:26:54', '<h1>Sustainability and Energy Consultancy</h1>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Our Building Consultancy team provides specific sustainability consultancy by devising and delivering low carbon solutions on new construction projects, existing buildings and estates strategies that lead the way in terms of best practice.</span></p>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">We survey buildings and estates to assess current energy performance levels before advising on practical strategies, which consider the lifecycle of an asset to improve energy and carbon performance whilst saving money.</span>  Working in close collaboration with our clients, we support bids for sustainable funding including the Government''s Salix funding and revolving higher education Green Fund schemes.</p>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">We help our clients achieve the following accreditations:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="p2"><span class="s4">BREEAM • </span><span class="s1">Code for Sustainable Homes • </span><span class="s4">Passivhaus</span></li>\r\n<li class="p1"><span class="s1">Energy Performance Certificates • </span><span class="s1">SBEM calculations and SAP assessment</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Sustainability Consultancy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sustainability-consultancy', '', '', '2014-11-11 09:29:28', '2014-11-11 09:29:28', '', 20, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?page_id=378', 3, 'page', '', 0),
(379, 1, '2014-10-29 20:26:54', '2014-10-29 20:26:54', '<h1>Sustainability and Energy Consultancy</h1>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley integrates sustainability into our service delivery on all of our projects, yet our Building Consultancy team also provides specific sustainability consultancy to help our clients'' achieve their targets. We devise and deliver low carbon solutions on new construction projects, existing buildings and estates strategies that lead the way in terms of best practice.</p>\r\n<p>We survey buildings and estates to assess current energy performance levels before advising on practical strategies, which consider the lifecycle of an asset to improve energy and carbon performance whilst saving money.</p>\r\n<p>Working in close collaboration with our clients, we support their bids for sustainable funding including the Government''s Salix funding and revolving higher education Green Fund schemes.</p>\r\n<p>Through the use of feasibility studies, estate surveys and improvement strategies, we help our clients achieve the following accreditations:</p>\r\n<p>· BREEAM · Code for Sustainable Homes · Passivhaus · Energy Performance Certificates · SBEM calculations and SAP assessments</p>', 'Sustainability Consultancy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '378-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-29 20:26:54', '2014-10-29 20:26:54', '', 378, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/378-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(380, 1, '2014-10-29 20:30:24', '2014-10-29 20:30:24', '<h1>Estates and Facilities Consultancy (FM)</h1>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Our team led by experienced chartered surveyor’s partner with and support clients in managing their core business through rationalising their assets and facilities.  We use secure, mobile, cloud based technologies and IT systems to ensure that together we achieve long term, value based solutions </span><span class="s2">through the following services:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="p2"><span class="s1">Asset appraisal and rationalisation • </span>Estate and property strategies and master plans</li>\r\n<li class="p2">Management support • Estate condition and multi-facet surveys</li>\r\n<li class="p2">Business case, funding and bid support • Maintenance and development programmes</li>\r\n<li class="p2">Sustainability and energy assessments</li>\r\n<li class="p2">Full design, management and property consultancy service</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Estates and Facilities Consultancy (FM)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'estates-and-facilities-consultancy-fm', '', '', '2014-11-11 11:31:10', '2014-11-11 11:31:10', '', 20, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?page_id=380', 4, 'page', '', 0),
(381, 1, '2014-10-29 20:30:24', '2014-10-29 20:30:24', '<h1>Estates and Facilities Consultancy (FM)</h1>\r\n<p>Property and asset related costs can account for a quarter of annual costs or many organisations. Bowman Riley Building Consultancy can help an organisation make an informed choice about asset management to deliver rationalised, efficient estates and support future financial planning.</p>\r\n<p>We use the latest cloud based technologies and IT systems to ensure that we achieve long term, value based solutions. Our services include:</p>\r\n<p>Asset appraisal and rationalisation · Estate and property strategies and master plans · Management support – estate assets · Estate condition and multi-facet surveys · Business case, funding and bid support · Procurement and IT systems ??? · Maintenance and development programmes · Sustainability and energy assessments · Full design, management and property consultancy service</p>\r\n<p>Contact: <br />Robin Holme MRICS MAPM 07718 523 822 robin.holme@bowmanriley.com <br />Debbie Lewis FRICS 07982 30778 debbie.lewis@bowmanriley.com</p>', 'Estates and Facilities Consultancy (FM)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '380-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-10-29 20:30:24', '2014-10-29 20:30:24', '', 380, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/380-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
