(391, 1, '2014-10-29 20:47:40', '2014-10-29 20:47:40', '<h1>Architecture and lead consultancy</h1>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Bowman Riley Healthcare is a specialist architecture team that has successfully delivered a range of projects across the health economy within the acute, primary, mental health, specialist and aged care clients for the public and private sectors.  Our track record as architects and lead consultants spans significant hospital developments, new and refurbished health centres to bespoke specialist care facilities for residential, care homes and dementia care.</span></p>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">We provide a range of services and proactive lean thinking to assist clients to deliver high quality, efficient, safe, innovative and practical solutions that offers best value and improves the patient experience through the built environment.</span></p>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Our team has extensive knowledge of the NHS Health Technical Memorandums (HTM) and Health Building Notes (HBN) to enhance our service offering.  We have in-house Activity Database (ADB) expertise and we have a detailed understanding of the Care Quality Commission (CQC) quality risk profiling, Premises Assurance Model (PAM) and other evidence-based design tools such as A Staff &amp; Patient Environment Calibration Tool (ASPECT) and Achieving Design Excellence Evaluation Tool Kit (AEDET).</span></p>', 'Architecture and lead consultancy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'architecture-and-lead-consultancy', '', '', '2014-11-10 18:29:47', '2014-11-10 18:29:47', '', 22, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?page_id=391', 0, 'page', '', 0),
