(399, 1, '2014-10-29 21:01:29', '2014-10-29 21:01:29', '22 August 2014\nBowman Riley Architects has reached the finals for two awards at the high profile Yorkshire Business Insider Awards 2014 to be held in Leeds in September 2014.\nThe company has been shortlisted in the prestigious Architecture Firm of the Year category competing and the retail development we designed at Albion Place, Skipton for Maplegrove Developments has been shortlisted for Development of the Year. \nThe Awards celebrate achievements across the built environment recognising the buildings, investors, developers, architects, consultants and contractors that that make significant contributions to the ever-changing Yorkshire skyline.\nThe glittering award ceremony takes place on 24 September 2014 at New Dock Hall, The Royal Armouries in Leeds.\n\n', 'Shortlisted at Yorkshire Insider Property Awards 2014', 'Bowman Riley Architects has reached the finals for two awards at the high profile Yorkshire Business Insider Awards 2014 to be held in Leeds in September 2014.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '68-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-10-29 21:01:29', '2014-10-29 21:01:29', '', 68, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/68-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
