(521, 1, '2014-10-30 11:24:50', '2014-10-30 11:24:50', '<h3>Westcliffe Medical Centre</h3>\r\n<p>Westcliffe Medical Centre is a long established Shipley practice, which is part of NHS Bradford and Airedale and Leeds Primary Care Trust cluster. The practice offers high quality care to its patients and as part of its commitment to improving the centre invested in refurbishment works.</p>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley Healthcare was commissioned directly by the practice to provide architecture and project management services for the internal refurbishment of the existing medical centre</p>\r\n<p>The works comprised the refurbishment of the reception and entrance areas and consulting rooms involving new reception desk, floor finishes, IPS panels and decorations.</p>\r\n<p>The project was successfully completed to Care Quality Commission (CQC) standards.</p>', 'Westcliffe Medical Centre', 'Westcliffe Medical Centre is a long established Shipley practice, which is part of NHS Bradford and Airedale and Leeds Primary Care Trust cluster. The practice offers high quality care to its patients and as part of its commitment to improving the centre invested in refurbishment works.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'westcliffe-medical-centre', '', '', '2014-11-11 12:48:36', '2014-11-11 12:48:36', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=casestudies&#038;p=521', 0, 'casestudies', '', 0),
