(523, 1, '2014-10-30 11:26:31', '2014-10-30 11:26:31', '<h3>Chigwell Medical Centre</h3>\r\n<p>The Chigwell Medical Centre has been serving an increasing list of patients from the local cross boundary communities between Redbridge and West Essex and the residents of three nearby care homes for over 30 years.</p>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley Healthcare was commissioned to design a single storey extension to the existing Medical Centre building. The new 60m² extension was designed to accommodate a new pharmacy facility.</p>\r\n<p>In addition, we designed significant external works to provide the medical centre with a fully accessible entrance to the building.</p>', 'GP Surveyors', 'The Chigwell Medical Centre has been serving an increasing list of patients from the local cross boundary communities between Redbridge and West Essex and the residents of three nearby care homes for over 30 years.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'gp-surveyors', '', '', '2014-11-11 14:10:11', '2014-11-11 14:10:11', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=casestudies&#038;p=523', 0, 'casestudies', '', 0),
