(529, 1, '2014-10-22 11:31:18', '2014-10-22 11:31:18', '<p>Bowman Riley Architects recently sponsored Skipton golfer, Malcolm Elrick in his bid to retain the European blind golf title.</p>\r\n<p>Malcolm came second in the prestigious European tournament.</p>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley organises a very popular annual golf day at Skipton Golf Club every June for clients, staff and friends of the company. Malcolm will present the winner of the 2015 Bowman Riley Golf Day the company’s trophy.</p>\r\n<p>Photo - Malcolm Elrick with Andrea Calcaterra, the tournament organiser and rest of the world captain</p>', 'Sponsoring the European Blind Golf Champion', 'Bowman Riley Architects recently sponsored Skipton golfer, Malcolm Elrick in his bid to retain the European blind golf title.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sponsoring-european-blind-golf-champion', '', '', '2014-10-30 11:32:34', '2014-10-30 11:32:34', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=news&#038;p=529', 0, 'news', '', 0),
(530, 1, '2014-10-30 11:32:28', '2014-10-30 11:32:28', '', 'Malcolm-Elrick-with-Andrea-calcaterra-the-tournament-organiser-and-rest-of-the-world-captain', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'malcolm-elrick-with-andrea-calcaterra-the-tournament-organiser-and-rest-of-the-world-captain', '', '', '2014-10-30 11:32:28', '2014-10-30 11:32:28', '', 529, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Malcolm-Elrick-with-Andrea-calcaterra-the-tournament-organiser-and-rest-of-the-world-captain.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(531, 1, '2014-10-29 11:33:59', '2014-10-29 11:33:59', '<p>Bowman Riley Healthcare formed part of the team involved in the refurbishment of a TB Hospital in Swaziland, which has just won the IHEEM Northcroft Silver Medal for Outstanding Contribution to the Advancement of Healthcare Engineering!</p>\r\n<p>We donated our time on a pro bono basis to design the refurbishment of the Good Shepherd Hospital following incidences of drug-resistant tuberculosis infecting healthcare workers.</p>\r\n<p>Working in collaboration with Bradford Teaching Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust, the University of Leeds and Apex4D, a low tech, low cost solution was introduced to this 21st century problem aimed at improving infection control.</p>\r\n<p>We redesigned the layout and the air flow at the hospital to control the spread of this airborne highly infectious disease.</p>\r\n<p>Our work was undertaken using Building Information Modelling (BIM) software to provide a 3D model and simulate the site, which enabled us to model the refurbishment from the UK without the need to survey the hospital in person.</p>', ' Infection Control in a Developing World ', 'Bowman Riley Healthcare formed part of the team involved in the refurbishment of a TB Hospital in Swaziland, which has just won the IHEEM Northcroft Silver Medal for Outstanding Contribution to the Advancement of Healthcare Engineering!', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'infection-control-developing-world', '', '', '2014-10-30 11:35:02', '2014-10-30 11:35:02', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=news&#038;p=531', 0, 'news', '', 0),
(532, 1, '2014-10-30 11:34:58', '2014-10-30 11:34:58', '', 'Staff-outside-the-Good-Shepherd-Hospital', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'staff-outside-the-good-shepherd-hospital', '', '', '2014-10-30 11:34:58', '2014-10-30 11:34:58', '', 531, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Staff-outside-the-Good-Shepherd-Hospital.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(533, 1, '2014-10-24 11:36:08', '2014-10-24 11:36:08', '<p>For the fifth consecutive year, Bowman Riley Architects has been selected as one of the top 50 companies to work for in the UK’s construction industry by Building magazine as featured in this month''s Good Employer Guide.</p>\r\n<p>Companies included in the guide stand out because of the benefits they offer their staff, ranging from training opportunities to career progression and a healthy work-life balance.</p>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley Architects recognises that investment in our people in terms of career development, staff satisfaction and a rewarding work environment is critical to the success of our business.</p>', 'Building Good Employer Guide 2014', 'For the fifth consecutive year, Bowman Riley Architects has been selected as one of the top 50 companies to work for in the UK’s construction industry by Building magazine as featured in this month''s Good Employer Guide.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'building-good-employer-guide-2014', '', '', '2014-10-30 11:36:40', '2014-10-30 11:36:40', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=news&#038;p=533', 0, 'news', '', 0),
