(545, 1, '2014-10-30 13:02:24', '2014-10-30 13:02:24', '<h3>Montagu Hospital</h3>\r\n<p>As part of framework agreement for architectural services with Doncaster &amp; Bassetlaw Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust, Bowman Riley Healthcare was commissioned to design the refurbishment and upgrade of two rehabilitation wards at Montagu Hospital in Barnsley.</p>\r\n<p>Our role involved reconfiguring the Adwick and Wentworth wards from six to four bedroom wards with the provision of new en-suite facilities.</p>\r\n<p>The refurbished wards have been designed to be bright, airy and conducive to the rehabilitation and the healing process.</p>', 'Doncaster & Bassetlaw Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust', 'As part of framework agreement for architectural services with Doncaster & Bassetlaw Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust, Bowman Riley Healthcare was commissioned to design the refurbishment and upgrade of two rehabilitation wards at Montagu Hospital in Barnsley.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'doncaster-bassetlaw-hospitals-nhs-foundation-trust', '', '', '2014-11-11 14:13:06', '2014-11-11 14:13:06', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=casestudies&#038;p=545', 0, 'casestudies', '', 0),
