(635, 1, '2014-11-05 17:32:57', '2014-11-05 17:32:57', '<h1>Coordinated<br /><em>Consultancy</em></h1>\r\n<p>We provide high quality coordinated project, management and property consultancy services that support our clients’ in achieving their built environment aspirations on new projects, refurbishment schemes and estates rationalisation.</p>\r\n<p>Our tailored solutions are applied with ingenuity through our main services, see below.</p>', 'Building Consultancy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-05 17:32:57', '2014-11-05 17:32:57', '', 20, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/20-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(636, 1, '2014-11-05 17:33:35', '2014-11-05 17:33:35', '<h1>Designing for change in<br /><em>Healthcare</em></h1>\r\n<p>Bowman Riley Healthcare Architects design high quality healthcare and social care environments that enhance the patient journey and focus on improved health outcomes.</p>\r\n<p>Designing new buildings, re-configuring existing properties and rationalising healthcare estates, the team provides solutions to the 21st century challenges of increasing efficiency, achieving cost savings and addressing the evolving clinical and patients’ needs.</p>\r\n<p>Working in collaboration with healthcare clients, government bodies, community healthcare partnerships, providers of aged and dementia care, academic institutions and leading industry professionals, we are at the forefront of healthcare design and innovation. Our team co-founded the Health BIM group working alongside the Department of Health, NHS and private sector partners on the Integrated Health Information Model.</p>\r\n<p>As a joint venture partner with TAHPI, we are the European partners of the Health Facility Briefing System, a web suite of integrated tools offered on a subscription basis to support the health industry.</p>', 'Healthcare', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '22-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-05 17:33:35', '2014-11-05 17:33:35', '', 22, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/22-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(637, 1, '2014-11-05 17:35:14', '2014-11-05 17:35:14', '<h1>COMMERCIALLY<br />CREATIVE <em>ARCHITECTS</em></h1>\r\n<p>A commitment to high quality and innovative design is at the very heart of the projects we create.</p>\r\n<p>With significant experience in the delivery of a wide range of new and refurbished buildings, we help our clients realise their built environment aspirations.</p>\r\n<p>From small complex projects to multi-million pound developments and roll-out programmes, our team has the practical expertise to take a project from concept planning to completion on site.</p>\r\n<p>Working in partnership with our clients and the wider design and construction team, we strive to lead the way in terms of innovation, efficiency and sustainability to deliver tangible benefits for our clients.</p>\r\n<p>Please explore our services and case studies for more information.</p>', 'Architects', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '18-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-05 17:35:14', '2014-11-05 17:35:14', '', 18, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/18-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
