(750, 1, '2014-11-10 17:04:32', '2014-11-10 17:04:32', '<p>BA (Hons), Dip Arch, RIBA</p>\r\n<p>Darren joined Bowman Riley Architects in 1991. He specialises in food retail developments and drives forward Bowman Riley’s operations overseas. He is responsible for the practice’s finance and IT management. Darren enjoys skiing, tennis and travel.</p>', 'Darren Bush', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'darren-bush', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:46:35', '2014-11-11 10:46:35', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=750', 0, 'people', '', 0),
