(752, 1, '2014-11-10 17:05:32', '2014-11-10 17:05:32', '<p>BA (Hons) DipArch (Oxford) RIBA                  </p>\r\n<p>John is a director with 25 years’ experience as an architect designing a variety of residential, hotel leisure, commercial and industrial buildings. By reputation, John has built up a client base comprising some of Yorkshire’s highest regarded business people. His recent track record includes: £20 million head office in Leeds, the award-winning Greenroyd Mills redevelopment, a Grade 1 listed hotel renovation in York city centre, the UK’s most technologically advanced soft drinks factory and one of the largest livestock farms in the country. Away from work, John enjoys riding his Italian motorbike across the North Yorkshire Moors and Lake District.</p>', 'John Coultas', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'john-coultas', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:44:37', '2014-11-11 10:44:37', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=752', 0, 'people', '', 0),
