(754, 1, '2014-11-10 17:06:20', '2014-11-10 17:06:20', '<p>BA Arch Dip Arch ARB</p>\r\n<p>Michael became a director of Bowman Riley Architects in 2014. Initially starting his career at Bowman Riley, Michael re-joined the company in 2009 after several years working in London. He specialises in the design and project management of developments in the retail, commercial and bio science sectors and champions modular construction. Out of the Office, Michael enjoys playing and coaching rugby, cycling and outdoor activities.</p>', 'Michael Feather', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'michael-feather', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:42:17', '2014-11-11 10:42:17', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=754', 0, 'people', '', 0),
