(756, 1, '2014-11-10 17:07:13', '2014-11-10 17:07:13', '<p>BA, BArch (Manchester) RIBA</p>\r\n<p>Laurence is director with responsibility for community, regeneration and education projects. He is passionate about design and quality and has a first class record in the successful delivery of complex projects. Over the years, Laurence has designed a number of award-winning buildings including: Albion Place retail development, Culture Fusion youth centre, Kirkstall Brewery student residences and the Civic Quarter Library and Gateway Building for Leeds Metropolitan University, which features in the Pevsner Architectural Guide to Leeds. Given the opportunity, Laurence would like to spend more time travelling and looking at maps.</p>', 'Laurence Teeney', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'laurence-teeney', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:41:47', '2014-11-11 10:41:47', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=756', 0, 'people', '', 0),
