(758, 1, '2014-11-10 17:07:51', '2014-11-10 17:07:51', '<p>BSc Hons</p>\r\n<p>Tony joined Bowman Riley Architects in 2007 and moved South in 2012 to manage the new central London office. He is currently developing new relationships in and around London as Bowman Riley continues to grow business in the South. Tony is currently involved in commercial, retail, petroleum and residential sectors. He is a keen footballer and snowboarder.</p>', 'Tony Pleasants', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tony-pleasants', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:41:22', '2014-11-11 10:41:22', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=758', 0, 'people', '', 0),
