(760, 1, '2014-11-10 17:10:55', '2014-11-10 17:10:55', '<p>Code for Sustainable Homes Assessor</p>\r\n<p>Promoted to Associate in 2012, Craig leads the technical delivery of a range of predominantly social housing and private residential developments. As a Code for Sustainable Homes Assessor, Craig promotes sustainable design and construction best practice by supporting clients to achieve environmental accreditations. He is a keen football fan and enjoys travel, live music and spending time with friends and family.</p>', 'Craig Savoury', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'craig-savoury', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:40:53', '2014-11-11 10:40:53', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=760', 0, 'people', '', 0),
