(762, 1, '2014-11-10 17:11:27', '2014-11-10 17:11:27', '<p>BA Hons Dip. Arch ARB</p>\r\n<p>Promoted to Associate in 2013, Andrew manages projects in the commercial, hotel and leisure, social and private housing sectors. His experience covers all aspects of project delivery from inception through to completion but his main skills lie in developing design concepts up to planning stage. Andrew’s current role involves leading a team to deliver a £20m new HQ office building in Leeds. Out of work, Andrew likes mountain biking, snowboarding, live music and cooking/eating good food.</p>', 'Andrew Wolstenholme', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'andrew-wolstenholme-2', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:40:22', '2014-11-11 10:40:22', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=762', 0, 'people', '', 0);
