(766, 1, '2014-11-10 17:13:38', '2014-11-10 17:13:38', '<p>David is a long standing member of the Bowman Riley team and was promoted to Associate in 2004. He has a wide range of experience in the delivery of projects in the residential, retail, commercial, education and hotels and leisure sectors including the renovation of a Grade I listed boutique hotel in York. He is a keen follower of Liverpool Football Club and enjoys watching live music.</p>', 'David Hodgson', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'david-hodgson', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:38:59', '2014-11-11 10:38:59', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=766', 0, 'people', '', 0),
