(770, 1, '2014-11-10 17:15:22', '2014-11-10 17:15:22', '<p>MA Dip Arch (Cantab) RIBA</p>\r\n<p>Anthony has 25 years’ experience as a qualified architect with excellent master planning and design skills. He focuses on front-end project work from client engagement through concept design to planning and beyond. He has an efficient, pragmatic approach to the design process and enjoys interaction with clients and consultants. Anthony has worked in the USA, China and India as well as the UK and has spent the last three years at Bowman Riley liaising with overseas clients. In his spare time, he enjoys hiking, mountain-biking, travel and photography.</p>', 'Anthony Barnett', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'anthony-barnett', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:38:16', '2014-11-11 10:38:16', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=770', 0, 'people', '', 0),
