(772, 1, '2014-11-10 17:16:02', '2014-11-10 17:16:02', '<p>BA (Hons) PGDipArch RIBA</p>\r\n<p>Colin has over seven years’ experience as an architect with considerable flair who excels in client engagement.   His experience ranges from commercial developments to private residential schemes and historic buildings. Colin won the Best Building Design Award for Yorkshire Dales National Park Authority. He fulfils the roles of RIBA York branch secretary and is a BREEAM Accredited Professional. Colin is fluent in French and Grade 8 pianist.</p>', 'Colin Briggs', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'colin-briggs', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:37:53', '2014-11-11 10:37:53', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=772', 0, 'people', '', 0),
