(774, 1, '2014-11-10 17:16:46', '2014-11-10 17:16:46', '<p>BA Hons, Dip. Arch</p>\r\n<p>Ruth has over 20 years’ experience designing community, education, commercial and historic buildings. She enjoys working closely with clients to fulfil every aspect of their brief and excels in user group, stakeholder and community consultation throughout the design process. Ruth was the project architect on two award-winning projects; the Henshaws Arts &amp; Crafts Centre in Knaresborough and Bright Beginnings Childcare Centre for University of Leeds. As a BREEAM Accredited Professional, she is committed embracing sustainable principles whilst producing designs which are efficient, workable and surpass expectations. Out of work, Ruth enjoys creating stained glass, painting watercolours and tennis.</p>', 'Ruth Bush', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ruth-bush', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:37:37', '2014-11-11 10:37:37', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=774', 0, 'people', '', 0),
