(776, 1, '2014-11-10 17:17:21', '2014-11-10 17:17:21', '<p>RIBA</p>\r\n<p>Anita joined Bowman Riley Architects in 2007. With an excellent track record in the successful delivery of a range of retail developments, Anita is a meticulous designer with a high level of attention to detail.   Outside of work, Anita is a fully qualified fitness studio instructor, who teaches a range of classes.</p>', 'Anita Rebaudo', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'anita-rebaudo', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:37:20', '2014-11-11 10:37:20', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=776', 0, 'people', '', 0),
