(778, 1, '2014-11-10 17:18:22', '2014-11-10 17:18:22', '<p>BA Hons PG Dip</p>\r\n<p>Craig is a qualified architect who loves to create exciting contemporary designs. He has particular strengths in the visual presentation of his design concepts. Craig drives forward the use of new technologies to enhance the delivery of our services including BIM, 3D visualisation and augmented reality. Craig’s experience is further strengthened through extensive travel around Asia, Australasia and South America.</p>', 'Craig Mewse', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'craig-mewse', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:36:30', '2014-11-11 10:36:30', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=778', 0, 'people', '', 0),
