(780, 1, '2014-11-10 17:18:57', '2014-11-10 17:18:57', '<p>BA (Hons) PGDipArch ARB</p>\r\n<p>Roy qualified as an architect in 2009 and since then he has designed and led a number of significant retail developments. Most recently he acted as project architect on the Albion Place retail development on Skipton High Street successfully delivering the scheme using Building Information Modelling (BIM). This project won ‘Development of the Year 2014’ in the Yorkshire Business Insider Property Awards. Roy enjoys playing and watching football.</p>', 'Roy Wilson', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'roy-wilson', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:35:21', '2014-11-11 10:35:21', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=780', 0, 'people', '', 0),
