(782, 1, '2014-11-10 17:21:30', '2014-11-10 17:21:30', '<p>BA (Hons) Dip Arch Pg Dip</p>\r\n<p>Biba joined Bowman Riley Healthcare in September 2013 after working for architectural practices in London for three years. As a recently qualified Architect, she has an enthusiastic and collaborative approach and excels at client engagement. Biba enjoys baking, cooking and traveling in her spare time.</p>', 'Biba Thacker', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'biba-thacker', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:31:56', '2014-11-11 10:31:56', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=782', 0, 'people', '', 0),
