(784, 1, '2014-11-10 17:23:21', '2014-11-10 17:23:21', '<p>Andy has considerable experience in the use of BIM using Revit Architecture to produce architectural models on a wide variety of projects with contract values ranging from £5 million to £60 million. He works with the wider design team to share BIM information for the overall benefit of the project delivery.   Andy has developed in-house best practice protocols for the use of Revit and produced standard templates. He is actively involved with the Bowman Riley BIM steering group, set up to facilitate the use of BIM in line with industry standards and clients’ expectations. In his spare time, Andrew enjoys mountain biking and walking.</p>', 'Andy Tate', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'andy-tate', '', '', '2014-11-10 17:23:21', '2014-11-10 17:23:21', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=784', 0, 'people', '', 0),
(785, 1, '2014-11-10 17:24:12', '2014-11-10 17:24:12', '<p>Kiran Joined Bowman Riley Healthcare in July 2014 bringing considerable experience of using Revit Architecture to produce architectural models on a wide variety of projects with contract values ranging from £3 million to £35 million. He is responsible for producing construction drawings and plays key role in understanding and resolving design and site queries through liaison with clients, contractors and consultants.   Kiran enjoys spending time with his family in his spare time.</p>', 'Kiran Parmar', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'kiran-parmar', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:56:26', '2014-11-11 10:56:26', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=785', 0, 'people', '', 0),
