(794, 1, '2014-11-10 19:24:29', '2014-11-10 19:24:29', '<h1>Our Story</h1>\r\n<p>In 1968 three architects decided to launch a new practice and unable to decide on where to locate the Head Office to best serve the commercial centres of Leeds and Manchester, a pin was stuck in a map somewhere in between. The market town Skipton, on the edge of the Yorkshire Dales was picked and there our story began.</p>\r\n<p>From the beginning the practice has had a very clear, unswerving, focus on quality design, attention to detail and client care, so much so that we continue to work with long standing clients, some of whom span back to our company’s inception.</p>\r\n<p>Today Bowman Riley is a dynamic and commercial practice led by directors Darren Bush, John Coultas, Michael Feather, Matthew Jones and Laurence Teeney operating from offices in Leeds, London and Skipton. To complement our design services, we offer a range of Building Consultancy services led by Robin Holme.</p>\r\n<p>In 2010 Steve Batson and Mark Dean joined our family and launched Bowman Riley Healthcare Architects to meet the needs of this specialist market.</p>', 'Our Story', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '6-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-10 19:24:29', '2014-11-10 19:24:29', '', 6, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/uncategorized/6-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
