(824, 1, '2014-11-11 10:29:32', '2014-11-11 10:29:32', '<p class="p1">Jonathan provides technical expertise and a keen eye for detail to facilitate the successful delivery of a wide range of healthcare projects.  At the forefront of technological advancements, he is driving the implementation of Building Information Modelling (BIM) and is involved the Integrated Health Model, which investigates the customisation of BIM specifically for the healthcare sector. </p>\r\n<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Outside of work, Jonathan enjoys watching rugby league and playing badminton.</span></p>', 'Jonathan Hazelgrave', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jonathan-hazelgrave', '', '', '2014-11-11 10:54:21', '2014-11-11 10:54:21', '', 0, 'http://92.60.114.159/~bowmanriley/?post_type=people&#038;p=824', 0, 'people', '', 0),
